@startuml
title Weather Station System State Machine

[*] --> RunningFromShutdown
state RunningFromShutdown
RunningFromShutdown --> INITIAL_STATE
INITIAL_STATE --> Configuration : changes or power-saving settings required
INITIAL_STATE --> DataCollection : triggered by clock
INITIAL_STATE --> StatusChecking : request
INITIAL_STATE --> WeatherSummaryRequested
INITIAL_STATE --> ShuttingDown
INITIAL_STATE --> ControlledModeOn

state RunningFromShutdown
RunningFromShutdown --> Configuration : changes or power-saving settings required
RunningFromShutdown --> DataCollection : triggered by clock
RunningFromShutdown --> StatusChecking : request
RunningFromShutdown --> WeatherSummaryRequested : summary prepared
RunningFromShutdown --> ShuttingDown : shutdown command given while running
RunningFromShutdown --> ControlledModeOn : remote control on

RunningFromShutdown --> Running : activity completed

state Configuration
Configuration --> Running : configuration completed

state DataCollecting
state StatusCheckingMode
state WeatherSummaryRequested
state ShuttingDown
state ControlledModeOn
state Running
@enduml
